  <brief_title>Post-op Ketamine Study</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluation of Post Operative Pain Following Primary Total Knee Arthroplasty (TKA) With Intraoperative Subanesthetic Ketamine Administration and Spinal Anesthesia</official_title>
  <sponsors>
